Title Review: Great concept but the app constantly gives messages as if I came in contact with a corona patient in a more elite city that I have never visited. Already 15 times in the last day. The location services operate as usual and identify me at home in Jerusalem. Update 2/4/2020 The app has already sent me 40 (not an exaggeration but the exact number) all incorrect identifications in the same place in a synagogue in Beitar Illit. It's stressful and frustrating and I'm considering removing the app please take care of it
